Time to get stoked about Terrain’s First Annual Winter BrrrZAAR!!!

CALL FOR SUBMISSIONS ARE NOW LIVE. THE EVENT WILL TAKE PLACE AT RIVER PARK SQUARE(Y’ALL THINK OF ALL THAT HOLIDAY FOOT TRAFFIC), ON ONE OF THE BUSIEST SHOPPING DAYS OF THE YEAR.
We are THRILLED to be partnering with River Park Square to make this happen. They also happen to be Winter BrrrZAAR’s Presenting Sponsor...THANK YOU!!! 

MORE DETAILS SOON.
